There was one other sighting in Wilmington on or around July 29th 2011
divs: Sighting Detailsapprox 11:30pm i went into my backyard and saw a very large orange light in the sky,i called inside to a friend and he came out and saw it.i went inside to find my video camera and when i went back outside my neighbors were also out in the front of my house looking at a second simliar object following the same course the first one went. both objects were observed by myself and 5 others.it made no sounds and it was like nothing i ever saw before !!!!
Summary: me and 5 other people saw 2 objects approx 2 min apart and go east to west!!!
